name: Converse Unisex Printed Black Shoes
description:
These low top shoes are inspired by converse's lucky charm Chuck Taylor - Basketball player turned salesman. Iconic and synonymous with style and youth culture, these shoes reflect a fusion of sport and style. These converse shoes have an improved comfort insole for better cushioned comfort for your feet. Central lacing system with a long tongue for comfort
Rubber overlay on the toe box to protect the toe region
Reinforced overlay at the heel region for good shoe structure
Metal eyelets on the midfoot for ventilation

Midsole
Contoured Latex foam insole newly developed by Converse to give added cushioning and comfort

Outsole
Rubber outsole with terraced grooves and patterned lugs

Make a paste using 1 tbsp of baking soda, 1 tbsp white vinegar and 1 tbsp hot water
Rub this paste onto the canvas and the sole using a brush
Wash off with lukewarm water
